FBIS4-35191 "drnes104dd_94009" FBIS-NES-94-104 Daily Report 28 May 1994 Palestinian Affairs 'Arafat To Retain Interior Minister's Post 'Arafat To Retain Interior Minister's Post LD2805142694 Rabat Moroccan Kingdom Radio Network in Arabic 1300 GMT 28 May 94 LD2805142694 Rabat Moroccan Kingdom Radio Network Arabic BFN [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Palestinian President Yasir 'Arafat has decided to retain the post of interior minister for himself. He will also head the forthcoming Palestinian Authority. The Palestinian leadership is expected to continue its meetings in Tunis today to appoint an information minister, as Hanan 'Ashrawi has turned this post down. [passage omitted]
